  "body": "I am using `debug_traceBlockByNumber` and `callTracer` to trace very old blocks. It is super fast at chainhead. However, it took 30 seconds to trace an old block (blocks in 2017). Are there any tricks to speed up the native tracer?\r\n\r\nNode storage has been upgraded to NVMe, but it did not boost the performance",
